race.comment: I AM PIETRA (5) is a first-starter by Pierata who was an AUD $25,000 (Magic Millions 2024 Gold Coast March Yearling Sale) purchase. Fitter for a recent trial placing and looks ready to run a big race. BRAVE IN SEATTLE (2) wasn't far away on debut last start over 1000m at Dalby, finishing second and beaten 1.1 lengths. Likely improver who is expected to be in the finish. PIPPIE POMAR (7) was prominent at the corner and finished second last start over 800m at Kilcoy, beaten half a length. Placed to advantage so expect a forward showing. THE WALKER'S ROSIE (9) is facing the starter for the first time but is sure to be well-educated out of the Schweida barn. Respect any market confidence.
